West of Zama Shrine once stood the {{ill|Hiranoya Meeting Hall|de|Hiranoya-Treffpunkt|ja|平野屋会所|zh|平野屋会所|qq=draft}}, which was demolished in 2008.<ref>[https://trystero.exblog.jp/7094448/ 大東市、平野屋新田会所が解体の危機 ]</ref>

